'''Albert Samama Chikly''' (24 Mutarama 1872 - 28 Ukuboza 1934), yari umukinnyi wa firime akaba n'umufotozi.  Ufatwa nk'imwe mu nkingi za mbere muri Sinema y'isi, Albert yari umufotozi, umukinnyi wa firime, technophile, adventure, umunyonzi w'amagare akaba n'umupayiniya wa  Seventh Art.i.  

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse ku ya 24 Mutarama 1872 i Tunisi, muri [[Tuniziya]], avukira mu muryango ukize wa Tuniziya ukomoka mu Bayahudi. Se David Samama, yari umunyamabanki wa Bey washinze ikigo cya banki nyuma gihinduka Banki ya [[Tuniziya]].  Nyina yari umugore wo mu rugo. Albert yakomereje amasomo ye hamwe na Charles Lavigerie hanyuma akorana n'Abayezuwiti i Marseille. Yari ingenzi yagiye muri Cape Horn, Ubushinwa na Ositaraliya kenshi ndetse akiri muto. Yakiriye izina rye 'Chikli' mu buvandimwe bw'abashinzwe kuzimya umuriro bo ku kirwa cya Chikly, ikirwa gito ku kiyaga cya Tuniziya . 

Yashakanye na Bianca Ferrero, umugore wavukiye mu [[Butaliyani]] ukomoka i Savoy, wari umucuranzi. <ref>Giulia Echites, [http://www.repubblica.it/spettacoli/cinema/2015/07/11/news/chikly-117675443/ "Visionario Chikly, portò il cinema (e la bicicletta) agli africani"] ''la Repubblica'' (11 July 2015).</ref> Abashakanye bari bafite umukobwa umwe Haydée Tamzali . Nyuma yaje kubona ubwenegihugu bw'Ubufaransa maze yinjira mu idini rya Isilamu n'umuryango we.

Albert yapfuye mu 1934 muri [[Tuniziya]] afite imyaka 62 ashyingurwa mu irimbi rya Borgel.
